  <div id="root" class="section1 content area">
    <div class="intro">
      <header>
          <div class="title">
            <%= image_tag '/images/circleme-y.png', class: "me in a circle frame" %>
            <div class="line-one"><h1>Hello,<strong> I'm Richard Enlow</strong></h1></div>
            <div class="line-two"><h2>A San Francisco based UX/UI Designer</h2></div>
          </div>
      </header>
      <div class="bio">
        <p>I'm specialised in Product Design, UI Design, UX Design, and Interaction with a firm foot in Visual Design and
          Front End Web Development (there is nothing more fulfilling than taking a mockup and coding it pixel-perfectly!).
          My passions are designing slick interfaces, frictionless user interaction, and adventure. I revel in the process and
          deliver top-notch, highly-accessible designs that look great and are easy to use.</p>

        <p>In my spare time, you can find me at shows (I'm a huge music fan) or chaperoning my dog
          <a href="http://instagram.com/ohiathedog" target="_blank"> (she's a party animal)</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

