          <p>A comprehensive hands-on course on User Research training including the initial stages of planning a User
            Research study and finding / qualifying participants. Conducting User Research tests including usability studies,
            diary studies, user interviews and more. Compiling and analyzing data to pull out findings and
            design concepts to present what was learned.
          </p>
